  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/TelephonyMessagingKit\/RCSService\/Business\/Card\/Media\/Height\ncrawled: 2025-12-13T03:45:12Z\n---\n\n# RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nEnumeration indicating the height of the media.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum Height\n```\n\n## Determining height\n\n- **RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height.short**: Short height.\n- **RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height.medium**: Medium height.\n- **RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height.tall**: Tall height.\n\n## Accessing card media properties\n\n- **url**: URL of media.\n- **contentType**: Content type of media.\n- **fileSize**: File size of media.\n- **thumbnailURL**: URL of thumbnail.\n- **thumbnailContentType**: Content type of thumbnail.\n- **thumbnailFileSize**: File size of thumbnail.\n- **displayHeight**: The display height for media.\n- **description**: Description of media.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- Copyable\n- Decodable\n- Encodable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
